lead_paragraph: Jack Harrison and Khiry Shelton scored two minutes apart in the second half and New York City FC beat the Columbus Crew 4-1 on Sunday to secure a first-round bye in the playoffs.

headline.print_headline: Villa Scores 23rd Goal, NYCFC Secures First-Round Bye
